To implement a guided process framework for user registration in ASP.NET Core with a single-page UI, follow these steps. The example will guide users through steps by highlighting fields, showing instructions, and enabling only the current step's fields.

---

### **1. Define the Model**
Create a model to hold all registration fields:
```csharp
public class UserRegistrationModel
{
    public string Name { get; set; }
    public string Email { get; set; }
    public string PhoneNumber { get; set; }
    public string Address { get; set; }
    public string Password { get; set; }
