```

---

### **2. Create the Razor View**
Design a single-page form with steps divided into sections. Use CSS to style the current step and disable others.

#### **`UserRegistration.cshtml`**
```html
@model YourApp.Models.UserRegistrationModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "User Registration";
}

<div class="container">
    <form id="registrationForm" method="post">
        <!-- Step 1: Personal Details -->
        <div class="step step1">
